        <updateDate>2021-03-10T11:48:22Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Help Ensure Legal Detainers Act or the HELD Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits the use of federal funds by a state or local subdivision that has in effect a law, policy, or procedure that prevents or impedes (1) a timely response to a request by the Department of Homeland Security for information about an alien in custody, including the alien's estimated release date; or (2) compliance with a detainer request.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
